@enumerate
@item
the library files are built by running the command:

@example
ikarus --compile-dependencies compile-all.sps
@end example

@noindent
with a system environment that allows Ikarus to find the relevant
libraries; this way the @fasl{} files are created in the source
directory of the project;

@item
the @fasl{} files are moved from the source directory into a
subdirectory of the build directory, preserving the directory structure.
@end enumerate


